info.description:
VCalSax is a simple Python module for managing calendaring data in XML. VCalSax
allows to load data from VCalendar files into DOM trees. And to rewrite such
trees as VCalendar files.
info.name: vcalsax
info.summary: VCal parser with a sax interface, written in Python
